'''DAUM''', the Institute for [[Dialectology]], [[Onomastic]]s and [[Folklore]] Research in [[Umeå]] ({{lang-sv|Dialekt-, ortnamns- och folkminnesarkivet i Umeå}}), is a [[Sweden|Swedish]] governmental archive bureau which collects, preserves, works up and provides information about dialects, place names, folklore culture and local history. DAUM is part of the [[Swedish Institute for Language and Folklore]].

